<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.3">
<l>tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉai viṇṇōr paravun talaimakaṉai tuḻāyviraip</l>
<l>pūmaruvi kaṇṇi yempirāṉaip poṉmalaiyai</l>
<l>nāmaruvi naṉkētti yuḷḷi vaṇaṅki nāmakiḻn tāṭa nāvalar</l>
<l>pāmaruvi niṟkat tanta pāṉmaiyē vaḷḷalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The generous man has a nature that grants us jointly praising [him] well</l>
<l>as lotus-eyed Kṛṣṇa, as the leader whom the celestials rever, as our lord</l>
<l>with a joint chaplet of fragrant Tulsi flowers, as a golden mountain,</l>
<l>thinking [of him], bowing, [our] tongues rejoicing [and] dancing,</l>
<l>[and grants] the tongue experts standing [there], bringing together metres.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
